cted account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,880],"id":"6d2bb640-4b0a-45ff-094d-db6fc6e6b7fd","name":"Note: Tag for Slow Nurture"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Wait Before Step 2\n\nPauses 2 days — spacing calls to respect rate limits.\n\nNext: Converted Already?","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"c13d9146-9cf3-ac27-b34e-2f7f3635fed1","name":"Note: Wait Before Step 2"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Converted Already?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.status }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Step 2 — Value Nudge (Outlook) · ②→ Mark Converted — Stop Drip","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"740451f4-3dfc-3b85-726c-6d5999690958","name":"Note: Converted Already?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Step 2 — Value Nudge (Outlook)\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Update Drip Status · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,280],"id":"38e915cd-7508-ab09-ccd0-1f52771a3b60","name":"Note: Step 2 — Value Nudge (Outlook)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Mark Converted — Stop Drip\n\nhubspot — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,880],"id":"953d3510-a28c-f729-6c53-4881cc845ca8","name":"Note: Mark Converted — Stop Drip"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Update Drip Status\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Completion Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"7617c026-1684-9188-bde5-f887d60153c0","name":"Note: Update Drip Status"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"fedea15d-bf58-665a-b536-2a12616ef25c","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"b472a1ed-5102-4ad0-0854-573e520e51ac","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\nhubspot — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"3232e01e-4d26-7c97-5b38-568f829d4194","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"b8e0f2d1-5934-8f32-f73e-50c7231d774b","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV